of which $13,421 and $17,199 were outstanding at December 31, 2008 and 2007,", "bbox": [150.0, 1240.7, 1053.4, 1266.1]}, {"text": "respectively.  The Facility expires in December 2010, and outstanding amounts bear interest at either (i)", "bbox": [150.0, 1267.1, 1108.4, 1292.4]}, {"text": "the prime rate or (ii) the London Interbank Offering Rate (“LIBOR”) plus Applicable Margin as defined", "bbox": [150.0, 1293.4, 1111.1, 1318.7]}, {"text": "within the Facility.  There were no borrowings under the Facility during 2008 and 2007.  At December", "bbox": [150.0, 1319.7, 1098.1, 1345.1]}, {"text": "31, 2008, there were no borrowing base limitations reducing the amount available to the Company for", "bbox": [150.0, 1346.1, 1090.8, 1371.4]}, {"text": "borrowings.", "bbox": [150.0, 1372.5, 277.3, 1397.8]}, {"text": "The Facility contains various affirmative and negative covenants.  The negative covenants", "bbox": [225.0, 1425.1, 1057.9, 1450.4]}, {"text": "include among others, certain limitations on transactions involving the creation of guarantees, sale of", "bbox": [150.0, 1451.5, 1081.6, 1476.8]}, {"text": "assets, acquisitions, mergers, investments and land purchases.  Additional covenants include (i) a", "bbox": [150.0, 1477.8, 1045.4, 1503.2]}, {"text": "minimum adjusted consolidated tangible net worth requirement, (ii) a maximum leverage ratio", "bbox": [150.0, 1504.2, 1022.6, 1529.5]}]}